		"description": "Complete API collection for the Notification System - A scalable, multi-channel notification service built with Spring Boot.\n\n## Features\n- Multi-channel notifications (EMAIL, SMS, PUSH, IN_APP)\n- Template-based messaging\n- Rate limiting with Redis (Token Bucket algorithm)\n- Channel-specific Kafka queues (Alex Xu design pattern)\n- Priority-based delivery\n\n## Channel-Specific Kafka Topics\nEach channel routes to its own Kafka topic for independent scaling:\n- `notifications.email` (3 partitions) - Email notifications\n- `notifications.sms` (2 partitions) - SMS notifications\n- `notifications.push` (4 partitions) - Push notifications\n- `notifications.in-app` (3 partitions) - In-app notifications\n- `notifications.dlq` (1 partition) - Dead Letter Queue\n\n## Base URL\n`http://localhost:8080`\n\n## Authentication\nCurrently no authentication required (development mode)",
